    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Victims & Attack Patterns\"\nformat: html\n---\n\n\n\n\n\n# üë• The People Behind the Patterns\n\nHumanitarian workers go where others can‚Äôt ‚Äî into war zones, disaster areas, and refugee camps.  \nBut when violence erupts, **who pays the highest price?**\n\nThis section confronts the human toll of these attacks.  \nNot just where or when they happen ‚Äî but **who** they hurt, **how** they suffer, and **what it means** for the future of humanitarian work.\n\n---\n\n## üßë‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è National vs. International Staff\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"plotly html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-ef97b6eca58651fb3aef\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-ef97b6eca58651fb3aef\">{\"x\":{\"data\":[{\"orientation\":\"v\",\"width\":0.89999999999999991,\"base\":0,\"x\":[1],\"y\":[884],\"text\":\"Worker Type: Internationals<br />Count:  884<br />Worker Type: Internationals\",\"type\":\"bar\",\"textposition\":\"none\",\"marker\":{\"autocolorscale\":false,\"color\":\"rgba(166,189,219,1)\",\"line\":{\"width\":1.8897637795275593,\"color\":\"transparent\"}},\"name\":\"Internationals\",\"legendgroup\":\"Internationals\",\"showlegend\":true,\"xaxis\":\"x\",\"yaxis\":\"y\",\"hoverinfo\":\"text\",\"frame\":null},{\"orientation\":\"v\",\"width\":0.90000000000000013,\"base\":0,\"x\":[2],\"y\":[7302],\"text\":\"Worker Type: Nationals<br />Count: 7302<br />Worker Type: Nationals\",\"type\":\"bar\",\"textposition\":\"none\",\"marker\":{\"autocolorscale\":false,\"color\":\"rgba(230,57,70,1)\",\"line\":{\"width\":1.8897637795275593,\"color\":\"transparent\"}},\"name\":\"Nationals\",\"legendgroup\":\"Nationals\",\"showlegend\":true,\"xaxis\":\"x\",\"yaxis\":\"y\",\"hoverinfo\":\"text\",\"frame\":null}],\"layout\":{\"margin\":{\"t\":43.762557077625573,\"r\":7.3059360730593621,\"b\":25.57077625570777,\"l\":48.949771689497723},\"font\":{\"color\":\"r